minance that covered two decades.\\u00c2 There are few athletes as universally loved as Nadal.\", \"from\": 22492, \"to\": 22611, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an incredible run\", \"from\": 22499, \"to\": 22516}, {\"ngram\": \"dominance\", \"from\": 22520, \"to\": 22529}, {\"ngram\": \"two decades\", \"from\": 22543, \"to\": 22554}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 22555, \"to\": 22556}, {\"ngram\": \"few athletes\", \"from\": 22567, \"to\": 22579}, {\"ngram\": \"Nadal\", \"from\": 22604, \"to\": 22609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even in the context of his rivalries, Nadal\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s quirks made him instantly unique beyond his tennis greatness.\", \"from\": 22612, \"to\": 22721, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the context\", \"from\": 22620, \"to\": 22631}, {\"ngram\": \"his rivalries\", \"from\": 22635, \"to\": 22648}, {\"ngram\": \"Nadal\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s quirks\", \"from\": 22650, \"to\": 22666}, {\"ngram\": \"his tennis greatness\", \"from\": 22700, \"to\": 22720}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He never left someone feeling bad and always knew how to put his impact in context.\", \"from\": 22722, \"to\": 22805, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 22736, \"to\": 22743}, {\"ngram\": \"his impact\", \"from\": 22783, \"to\": 22793}, {\"ngram\": \"context\", \"from\": 22797, \"to\": 22804}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Saying goodbye is bittersweet, but we know Nadal will find more greatness to come.\", \"from\": 22806, \"to\": 22888, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22849, \"end\": 22854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2013_Rafael_Nadal_tennis_season\", \"score\": 0.7430400134409658, \"rank\": 0.3458225424079517, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2013_Rafael_Nadal_tennis_season\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2013_Rafael_Nadal_tennis_season\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"goodbye\", \"from\": 22813, \"to\": 22820}, {\"ngram\": \"more greatness\", \"from\": 22865, \"to\": 22879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The year 2024 would be the 10th year of Xavier Schauffele\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s professional golf career.\", \"from\": 22890, \"to\": 22977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22930, \"end\": 22936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xavier_Musketeers_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 0.7772099123490598, \"rank\": 0.2802789932875607, \"text\": \"Xavier\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xavier_Musketeers_men's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xavier_Musketeers_men's_basketball\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The year\", \"from\": 22890, \"to\": 22898}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10th year\", \"from\": 22913, \"to\": 22926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has done quite a bit during his time on the big stage.\", \"from\": 22978, \"to\": 23035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"quite a bit\", \"from\": 22990, \"to\": 23001}, {\"ngram\": \"his time\", \"from\": 23009, \"to\": 23017}, {\"ngram\": \"the big stage\", \"from\": 23021, \"to\": 23034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He won the Olympic gold medal at the 2020 Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 23036, \"to\": 23093, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic gold medal\", \"from\": 23043, \"to\": 23065}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2020 Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 23069, \"to\": 23092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He put together a Rookie of the Year season between 2016 and 2017, including a bogey-free round of 66 at the U.S. Open.\", \"from\": 23094, \"to\": 23213, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a Rookie\", \"from\": 23110, \"to\": 23118}, {\"ngram\": \"the Year season\", \"from\": 23122, \"to\": 23137}, {\"ngram\": \"a bogey-free round\", \"from\": 23171, \"to\": 23189}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. Open\", \"from\": 23199, \"to\": 23212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had done a lot, including wins across the tour, but it seemed like he needed to make a change to get a win at a major.\", \"from\": 23214, \"to