7265, \"to\": 27280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We love to see greatness, and UConn was producing that at a level we haven\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t seen since John Calipari could actually win a championship.\", \"from\": 27306, \"to\": 27444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 27336, \"end\": 27341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UConn_Huskies_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 0.6082429176891152, \"rank\": 0.49324340613770284, \"text\": \"UConn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UConn_Huskies_men's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UConn_Huskies_men's_basketball\"}, {\"begin\": 27396, \"end\": 27409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Calipari\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Calipari\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Calipari\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Calipari\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"greatness\", \"from\": 27321, \"to\": 27330}, {\"ngram\": \"a level\", \"from\": 27364, \"to\": 27371}, {\"ngram\": \"a championship\", \"from\": 27429, \"to\": 27443}]}, {\"sentence\": \"UConn became the first back-to-back champion since Florida did it in 2007.\", \"from\": 27445, \"to\": 27519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 27445, \"end\": 27450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UConn_Huskies_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 0.6082429176891152, \"rank\": 0.49324340613770284, \"text\": \"UConn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UConn_Huskies_men's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UConn_Huskies_men's_basketball\"}, {\"begin\": 27496, \"end\": 27503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 0.9996581625475064, \"rank\": 0.00024550144611265704, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators_men's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators_men's_basketball\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"back\", \"from\": 27476, \"to\": 27480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was so much to love about this team, as UConn players represented four of the five all-Final Four team.\\u00c2 For those who don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t know much about the game of rugby, the Paris Olympics were a perfect introduction to this beautiful game.\", \"from\": 27520, \"to\": 27759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 27566, \"end\": 27571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UConn_Huskies_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 0.6082429176891152, \"rank\": 0.49324340613770284, \"text\": \"UConn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UConn_Huskies_men's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UConn_Huskies_men's_basketball\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this team\", \"from\": 27552, \"to\": 27561}, {\"ngram\": \"the five all-Final Four team\", \"from\": 27600, \"to\": 27628}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 27629, \"to\": 27630}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 27669, \"to\": 27677}, {\"ngram\": \"rugby\", \"from\": 27681, \"to\": 27686}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 27688, \"to\": 27706}, {\"ngram\": \"a perfect introduction\", \"from\": 27712, \"to\": 27734}, {\"ngram\": \"this beautiful game\", \"from\": 27738, \"to\": 27757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s known as one of the toughest sports in existence, but the flow of the sport in amazing.\", \"from\": 27760, \"to\": 27859, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 27765, \"to\": 27771}, {\"ngram\": \"the toughest sports\", \"from\": 27788, \"to\": 27807}, {\"ngram\": \"existence\", \"from\": 27811, \"to\": 27820}, {\"ngram\": \"the flow\", \"from\": 27826, \"to\": 27834}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 27838, \"to\": 27847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The way the game is structured opens the door for epic moments, and as the U.S. Women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Rugby team was looking to make an improbable run at a medal, we learned just how epic these moments can be.\\u00c2 The Americans were taking on Australia, with the winner taking the bronze medal in Rugby 7s.\", \"from\": 27860, \"to\": 28152, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 28060, \"end\": 28073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"score\": 0.9999999999407692, \"rank\": 3.5311572814273275e-11, \"text\": \"The Americans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 28089, \"end\": 28098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9908856498669908, \"rank\": 0.00513379171904606, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The way\", \"from\": 27860, \"to\": 27867}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 27868, \"to\": 27876}, {\"ngram\": \"the door\", \"from\": 27897, \"to\": 27905}, {\"ngram\": \"epic moments\", \"from\": 27910, \"to\": 27922}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 27931, \"to\": 27939}, {\"ngram\": \"Rugby team\", \"from\": 27950, \"to\": 27960}, {\"ngram\": \"an improbable run\", \"from\": 27981, \"to\": 27998}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 28002, \"to\": 28009}, {\"ngram\": \"these moments\", \"from\": 28036, \"to\": 28049}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 28057, \"to\": 28058}, {\"ngram\": \"the winner\", \"from\": 28104, \"to\": 28114}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze medal\", \"from\": 28122, \"to\": 28138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia was on the doorstep of a score that would put the U.S. out of reach, but then the impossible happened.\", \"from\": 28153, \"to\": 28265, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 28153, \"end\": 28162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9908856498669908, \"rank\": 0.00513379171904606, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the doorstep\", \"from\": 28170, \"to\": 28182}, {\"ngram\": \"a score\", \"from\": 28186, \"to\": 28193}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 28209, \"to\": 28217}, {\"ngram\": \"reach\", \"from\": 28225, \"to\": 28230}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alex \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSpiff\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Sedrick found a seam in the defense and went coast to coast with no one to stop her.\\u00c2 The U.S. quickly went from down 12-7 to up 12-12 with no time remaining.\", \"from\": 28266, \"to\": 28442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 28266, \"end\": 28270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.9978153813562992, \"rank\": 0.0021148461355877473, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a seam\", \"from\": 28297, \"to\": 28303}, {\"ngram\": \"the defense\", \"from\": 28307, \"to\": 28318}, {\"ngram\": \"coast\", \"from\": 28337, \"to\": 28342}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 28348, \"to\": 28354}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 28367, \"to\": 28368}, {\"ngram\": \"The U.S.\", \"from\": 28369, \"to\": 28377}, {\"ngram\": \"no time\", \"from\": 28423, \"to\": 28430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The insane ending did not end on the score, as the U.S. normal kicker was subbed off.\", \"from\": 28443, \"to\": 28528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The insane ending\", \"from\": 28443, \"to\": 28460}, {\"ngram\": \"the score\", \"from\": 28476, \"to\": 28485}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. normal kicker\", \"from\": 28490, \"to\": 28512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, Sedrick had to kick her own conversion, and she delivered to make it 14-12 to end the game.\\u00c2 As far as moments go, this might be the top one from the Olympics when it comes singular plays.\", \"from\": 28529, \"to\": 28722, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sedrick\", \"from\": 28533, \"to\": 28540}, {\"ngram\": \"her own conversion\", \"from\": 28553, \"to\": 28571}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 28615, \"to\": 28623}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 28624, \"to\": 28625}, {\"ngram\": \"moments\", \"from\": 28636, \"to\": 28643}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 28679, \"to\": 28691}, {\"ngram\": \"singular plays\", \"from\": 28706, \"to\": 28720}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was as exciting a 10 seconds as we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve seen this summer.\", \"from\": 28723, \"to\": 28783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve\", \"from\": 28758, \"to\": 28765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If it was for a gold medal, it would definitely be in the top 10.\", \"from\": 28784, \"to\": 28849, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 28798, \"to\": 28810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The year was 1992.\", \"from\": 28851, \"to\": 28869, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The year\", \"from\": 28851, \"to\": 28859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Silence of the Lambs changed how we look at horror thrillers, winning Best Picture in the process.\", \"from\": 28870, \"to\": 28972, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 28944, \"end\": 28956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Academy_Award_for_Best_Picture\", \"score\": 0.9999997303248529, \"rank\": 2.3325339225169541e-07, \"text\": \"Best Picture\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Academy_Award_for_Best_Picture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Academy_Award_for_Best_Picture\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Silence\", \"from\": 28870, \"to\": 28881}, {\"ngram\": \"the Lambs\", \"from\": 28885, \"to\": 28894}, {\"ng