925, \"to\": 32942}, {\"ngram\": \"a 36-yard touchdown pass\", \"from\": 32947, \"to\": 32971}, {\"ngram\": \"the third quarter\", \"from\": 32990, \"to\": 33007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The offense did not let Alabama feel comfortable, as Diego Pavia outplayed Jalen Milroe.\", \"from\": 33009, \"to\": 33097, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 33033, \"end\": 33040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alabama_Crimson_Tide\", \"score\": 0.9967550233106918, \"rank\": 0.0032446778792846282, \"text\": \"Alabama\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alabama_Crimson_Tide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alabama_Crimson_Tide\"}, {\"begin\": 33062, \"end\": 33067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\", \"score\": 0.9978539320924937, \"rank\": 0.0021436840076535335, \"text\": \"Diego\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\"}, {\"begin\": 33068, \"end\": 33073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pallacanestro_Pavia\", \"score\": 0.9467121987346188, \"rank\": 0.04793382364499279, \"text\": \"Pavia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pallacanestro_Pavia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pallacanestro_Pavia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The offense\", \"from\": 33009, \"to\": 33020}, {\"ngram\": \"Jalen Milroe\", \"from\": 33084, \"to\": 33096}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the first time Vanderbilt beat the number one team in the country, and it was the first Vanderbilt win over Alabama since 1984.\", \"from\": 33099, \"to\": 33233, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 33214, \"end\": 33221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alabama_Crimson_Tide\", \"score\": 0.9967550233106918, \"rank\": 0.0032446778792846282, \"text\": \"Alabama\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q2422