\": 33543}, {\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 33574, \"to\": 33582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Star players were rarely stealing bases, especially those who were mainly home run hitters.\", \"from\": 33615, \"to\": 33706, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Star players\", \"from\": 33615, \"to\": 33627}, {\"ngram\": \"bases\", \"from\": 33649, \"to\": 33654}, {\"ngram\": \"especially those\", \"from\": 33656, \"to\": 33672}, {\"ngram\": \"home run hitters\", \"from\": 33689, \"to\": 33705}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were less singles, too, as players are prioritizing extra-base hits and home runs.\\u00c2 It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s even crazier that this record was broken by a guy who\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s also one of the best pitchers in the league.\", \"from\": 33707, \"to\": 33907, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"less singles\", \"from\": 33718, \"to\": 33730}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 33740, \"to\": 33747}, {\"ngram\": \"extra-base hits\", \"from\": 33765, \"to\": 33780}, {\"ngram\": \"home runs\", \"from\": 33785, \"to\": 33794}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 33795, \"to\": 33803}, {\"ngram\": \"this record\", \"from\": 33822, \"to\": 33833}, {\"ngram\": \"a guy\", \"from\": 33848, \"to\": 33853}, {\"ngram\": \"the best pitchers\", \"from\": 33874, \"to\": 33891}, {\"ngram\": \"the league\", \"from\": 33895, \"to\": 33905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, Shohei Ohtani didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t pitch this season as he was recovering from an injury, but it showed what he could be if he focuses on one thing.\", \"from\": 33908, \"to\": 34055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 33919, \"end\": 33932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shohei_Ohtani\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shohei Ohtani\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shohei_Ohtani\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shohei_Ohtani\"}], \"no