to\": 44190}, {\"ngram\": \"her coaches\", \"from\": 44219, \"to\": 44230}, {\"ngram\": \"some very nefarious bribery claims\", \"from\": 44236, \"to\": 44270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the biggest storyline out of Tokyo was Simone Biles, who taught all non-gymnasts about the Twisties, and she was forced to step away from many of the events.\\u00c2 Come 2024, most gymnasts would be long retired if they were Biles\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 age.\", \"from\": 44272, \"to\": 44514, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 44310, \"end\": 44315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999816583940156, \"rank\": 1.1113055572969051e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 44320, \"end\": 44332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the biggest storyline\", \"from\": 44281, \"to\": 44302}, {\"ngram\": \"all non\", \"from\": 44345, \"to\": 44352}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnasts\", \"from\": 44353, \"to\": 44361}, {\"ngram\": \"the Twisties\", \"from\": 44368, \"to\": 44380}, {\"ngram\": \"the events\", \"from\": 44427, \"to\": 44437}, {\"ngram\": \"most gymnasts\", \"from\": 44451, \"to\": 44464}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 age\", \"from\": 44500, \"to\": 44512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 27 years old, while most gymnasts end their careers not long after they turn 21.\", \"from\": 44515, \"to\": 44603, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 44515, \"to\": 44522}, {\"ngram\": \"most gymnasts\", \"from\": 44543, \"to\": 44556}, {\"ngram\": \"their careers\", \"from\": 44561, \"to\"